Date: Sun, 27 Jul 2025 21:12:17 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 6/8] QSDK: CP: hostapd: ATF: Add distribution algo trigger
 timer

Airtime distribution occurs when any station joins/leaves and
when commitatf is issued. So, once any station joins/leave
trigger the algorithm.

ATF algorithm overview:
	1. trigger timer
	2. On timer expiry, start algorithm
	3. build the candidate list
	4. distribute the airtime based on the candidate list
	5. send to driver

Add apis to trigger atf distribution logic during station join/leave
and store the flags, which would be later used to update to the driver.

Remove the static keyword to change the scope of the function
hostapd_iface_num_sta(), so that it can be used by atf distribution
logic.

Signed-off-by: Harshitha Prem <hprem@qti.qualcomm.com>
